data.description: Looking for Space and a Fabulous location? Look no further! You'll love being only blocks to downtown Mishawaka, Central Park & the Riverwalk, plus easy access to Grape Rd! Greeted with a welcoming front porch, the home opens to a large living room with semi open den.  Nicely remodeled kitchen with flat panel cabinetry, stone counter tops with tile backsplash and stainless appliance package.  Open to the kitchen is the large dining area, perfect for all those holiday meals! The 5th bedroom completes the main level.  Up a few steps is a Huge primary bedroom complete with walk in closet and private ensuite bathroom.  Upstairs are the other 3 nice size bedrooms, laundry room and full hall bathroom with tiled tub surround.  The lower level features a daylight family room, 3rd full bathroom and bonus room.  Just out the kitchen door is a nice deck with firepit overlooking the fenced backyard.  Oversized 2 car detached garage with alley access.  Act fast!
